## influxDB+telegraf 

```
- cpu[units: percent (out of 100)]
    - usage_guest      float
    - usage_guest_nice float
    - usage_idle       float
    - usage_iowait     float
    - usage_irq        float
    - usage_nice       float
    - usage_softirq    float
    - usage_steal      float
    - usage_system     float
    - usage_user       float
- disk
    - free         integer
    - inodes_free  integer
    - inodes_total integer
    - inodes_used  integer
    - total        integer
    - used         integer
    - used_percent float
- diskio
    - io_time          integer
    - iops_in_progress integer
    - read_bytes       integer
    - read_time        integer
    - reads            integer
    - weighted_io_time integer
    - write_bytes      integer
    - write_time       integer
    - writes           integer
- kernel
    - boot_time        integer
